 178     pMaxGenerationByFuel(z,tech,f,y)                      'Max annual generation by zone-tech-fuel [GWh]'
 179     pFuelPrice(c,f,y)                                     'Fuel price forecasts'
 180   
 181  * Storage and transmission
 182     pNewTransmission(z,z2,pTransmissionHeader)           'New transmission line specifications'
 183   
 184  * Trade parameters
