1100     commtransmission(z,z2) 'Committed transmission corridors'
1101     cs(g)                  'Concentrated solar power units'
1102     so(g)                  'PV plants paired with storage'
1103     stp(g)                 'Dedicated storage blocks for PV plants'
1104     st(g)                  'All storage technologies (incl. standalone)'
