1166  * -------------------------------------------------------------
1167  Parameter
1168     pAllHours(q,d,y,t)           'All operating hours (used for peak tracking)'
1169     pFindSysPeak(y)              'Yearly system peak indicator'
1170     pSeasonalReporting           'Enable seasonal report outputs'
1171     fEnableInternalExchange      'Allow internal zone trading'
