1230     pFuelCarbonContent(f)          'Fuel carbon intensity (tCO₂/MMBtu)'
1231   
1232  * Economic parameters
1233     pRR(y)                         'Discount factor (accumulated)'
1234     pWACC                          'Weighted average cost of capital'
1235     pCRF(g)                        'Capital recovery factor (generator)'
